WEBVTT

1
00:23:17.250 --> 00:23:18.290 
乔治
George.

2
00:23:20.660 --> 00:23:22.130 
贝拉  谢谢你
Bella, thank you so much.

3
00:23:23.790 --> 00:23:24.580 
谢谢你  贝拉
Thank you, Bella,

4
00:23:24.580 --> 00:23:26.480 
但我不能揽下所有功劳
but I can't take all the credit.

5
00:23:26.490 --> 00:23:28.440 
亚当也应当被赞扬
Some of it has to go to Adam.

6
00:23:30.200 --> 00:23:32.270 
夏娃  夏娃
Eve! Eve!

7
00:23:32.490 --> 00:23:34.500 
我是指亚当和夏娃
I meant Adam and Eve.

8
00:23:34.500 --> 00:23:36.050 
夏娃是被陷害的
Eve was framed!

9
00:23:36.910 --> 00:23:39.090 
对  谢谢提醒
Yes, yes, thank you for that.

10
00:23:39.170 --> 00:23:41.240 
我的朋友们  我们正在岔路口
You know, my friends, we're at a crossroads...

11
00:23:41.370 --> 00:23:43.660 
我懂  "头发越高  离上帝越近"
I know, "the higher the hair, the closer to God",

12
00:23:43.660 --> 00:23:46.480 
但我应该给她弥补错误的机会
but I think I need to give her the chance to make amends.

13
00:23:46.880 --> 00:23:49.690 
当然了  如果我说的话
But of course, if I say something...

